10/11/83  read_mail (forward) request:  debug_mode

Syntax:  debug_mode {-control_args}


Function:  enables or disables the forward request's debugging
facilities.


Control arguments:
-on
   enables the forward request's debugging facilities.  (Default)
-off
   disables the forward request's debugging facilities.


Notes:
This request is intended for use only by read_mail developers.
